  {
    "title": "Story",
    "depth": 0,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "\"Once an eccentric master smith, but now an avenger siding with the Abyss.\""
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "The once-revered master craftsman was now known as the notorious Executioner of the Abyss, but Terizla didn't care."
          },
          {
            "text": "From the moment he was framed as a heretic by the Church, he had been wielding his hammer solely for revenge, for the day he could at last soothe the restless souls of his kin."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
